latestPosts.caption:
My recent craving for a good biryani was amazingly catered by @rdbdhabaguwahati . When it comes to North Indian Food they are the Real OG’s. After ages I finally found back the lost taste of biryani all thanks to @rdbdhabaguwahati . They had a wide range of North Indian dishes to choose from and I couldn’t help myself but to order my favourites. 

 🍽️I feasted to……..
➡️A Refreshing Bottle of the famous Goli Soda
➡️An amazing Plate of Shahi Chicken 
➡️All time star the Kolkata Dum Biryani
➡️The most comforting food The Daal Makhani
➡️Spicy Tawa chana Biryani to satisfy the spice lover within me
➡️Enjoyed the tender pieces of the legendary Paneer Butter masala
➡️Amazingly Prepared Chicken Tikka Basanti
➡️Soft and fulfilling Naan roti 
➡️An to top it all, I ended my great lunch feast with a tempting bowl of Gulkand Kheer.

Thank you 🙏🏻 @rdbdhabaguwahati for such a great time, enjoyed each and every moment there❤️
